    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Extremely sensitive gas chromatography detectors that allow man-made chemicals to be detected in low concentrations through the attachment of electrons via electron capture ionization.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
